    client: "OCAD University",
    descriptiontop:
    "OCAD University’s Ambient Experience Research Lab saw a lack of self reflection, or revisiting work and feedback from design students post-critique. Through a developed framework of design competencies, I led a team to impact the lab’s new goal of <b>improving student sharing about learning through a low-stake digital environment.</b>",
      descriptionbottom:
