{{
  await comp.ProjectOverview({
    title: "Reducing pressure through clear instructional materials",
    client: "Eve Medical",
    descriptiontop:
    "One of my first internship and freelance positions was with Eve Medical, a startup through another OCAD University graduate. Sampling for HPV and cervical cancer is a uncomfortable and sometimes anxiety-inducing experience. Traditional pap-smears are a uncomfortable experience for many women worldwide, and EveKit was a great solution. But all good products are at risk of not working well if functionality is unclear.",
      descriptionbottom:
    "Through careful audit and review of the product and existing training materials, I mapped out and remade the educational and training materials that went into the kit to provide <b> step by step directions for using the kit, aimed specifically at reducing pressure and calmly guiding women through the at-home screening</b>",
